# How to setup?

## Node.js
You can use node version manager to easily maintain your node version installation https://github.com/creationix/nvm

## Mosca module
Follow the installation tutorial (follow the embedded one) on https://github.com/mcollina/mosca

## Mosquitto
I use mosca broker module along with mosquitto as 'helper' broker. You can download and install mosquitto from http://mosquitto.org/download/

## MySQL module
I use MySQL database for logging and storing user and device's data.
Follow the installation tutorial on https://github.com/mysqljs/mysql
